&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 サンタ・モニカの山地とハーモサビーチのピアに沈む夕日。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><summary type="html">Sun sets behind the Santa Monica mountains and the Hermosa Beach Pier.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2207_A7R00294-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2207_A7R00294-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Golden Hour for Equality</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220626/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Golden Hour for Equality" /><published>2022-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/golden-rights</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220626/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
