  &lt;/div&gt;   
  &lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Lifeguard Towers" /><summary type="html">The sun reflects off the 15th St. lifeguard tower, painted in rainbow colors, in support of LGBQT rights.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09960.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09960.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Red &amp;amp; Orange</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220623/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Red &amp;amp; Orange" /><published>2022-06-23T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-23T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/red-and-orange</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220623/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The day’s clouds (&lt;a href=&quot;/220622/&quot;&gt;see previous photo&lt;/a&gt;) hung around until after sunset, creating this beautiful orange panorama sky, at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
今日の雲（&lt;a href=&quot;/220622/&quot;&gt; 前の写真参照&lt;/a&gt;）は日没まで残り、ハーモサビーチの5th St.でこの美しいオレンジ色の空のパノラマを作りました。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Clouds" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html">The day’s clouds (see previous photo) hung around until after sunset, creating this beautiful orange panorama sky, at 5th St. in Hermosa Beach.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09782-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09782-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Blue &amp;amp; Green</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220622/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Blue &amp;amp; Green" /><published>2022-06-22T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-22T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/blue-and-green</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220622/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
After morning rain, cumulus clouds fill the sky, in this oversaturated view of south Hermosa Beach from the pier.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
朝の雨上がり、積乱雲が空いっぱいに広がる。桟橋から見たHermosa Beach南部の風景です。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Clouds" /><summary type="html">After morning rain, cumulus clouds fill the sky, in this oversaturated view of south Hermosa Beach from the pier.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09699.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09699.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Strand Grasses</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220621/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Strand Grasses" /><published>2022-06-21T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-21T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/strand-grass</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220621/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Setting sun illuminates the grasses growing along the Strand, in front of the Manhattan Beach Pier.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    

マンハッタンビーチのピア前のストランドに生える草を照らす夕日。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">Setting sun illuminates the grasses growing along the Strand, in front of the Manhattan Beach Pier.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09568-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09568-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunset at 22nd St.</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220619/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset at 22nd St." /><published>2022-06-19T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2022-06-19T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/twentysecond</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220619/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  A clear evening, rare in June. It&apos;s a few days before the summer equinox, so the sun is far to the north, and sets over the Malibu coast.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 &lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
6月には珍しい晴天の夕方。夏至の数日前なので、太陽は北のマリブ海岸の上に沈んでいる。
  &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html">A clear evening, rare in June. It&apos;s a few days before the summer equinox, so the sun is far to the north, and sets over the Malibu coast.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09415-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2206_A7R09415-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>